  "accessibility_notes": "Rapid flashing is a serious WCAG/seizure risk. Keep any blink SLOW (>1s), never use on essential content, and disable entirely under prefers-reduced-motion (handled here). Honestly: prefer not to use blinking at all outside of nostalgia pieces.",
